1. Želim da iznajmim *apartman* za letovanje. (I want to rent an *apartment* for the summer vacation.)
2. U *apartmanu* ima klima uređaj i terasa sa pogledom na more. (The *apartment* has air conditioning and a terrace with a sea view.)
3. Naš *apartman* se nalazi u centru grada, u blizini svih važnih objekata. (Our *apartment* is located in the city center, near all important facilities.)
4. *Apartmani* na plaži su obično skuplji od onih u gradu. (The *apartments* on the beach are usually more expensive than those in the city.)
5. Iznajmljivanje *apartmana* je popularan vid smeštaja tokom turističke sezone. (Renting *apartments* is a popular form of accommodation during the tourist season.)
6. Moramo kupiti nove krevete za *apartmane* jer su postojeći dotrajali. (We need to buy new beds for the *apartments* because the existing ones are worn out.)
7. Uredili smo *apartmane* u našoj vili tako da se gosti osećaju kao kod kuće. (We have furnished the *apartments* in our villa so that guests feel at home.)
8. Naši *apartmani* su opremljeni modernim nameštajem i svim potrebnim uređajima. (Our *apartments* are equipped with modern furniture and all necessary appliances.)
9. Svakog leta iznajmljujem svoj *apartman* kako bih zaradila dodatni novac. (Every summer I rent out my *apartment* to earn extra money.)
10. Ovaj *apartmanski* kompleks ima bazen i restoran za goste. (This *apartment* complex has a pool and a restaurant for guests.)